data.description: Beautiful home all up graded inside. Kitchen has Energy star appliances and corian countertops. Home has lots of Pot shelves.  Tile floors through out, and carpet in bedrooms, The windows all have plantation shutters.  The solar is  owned.  The home has low E windows, and a new Anderson slider to the patio.  The 3 car garage has split AC. and is boat deep 35 ft on one side,  and the 21 x 36 RV carport has electricity.all wired underground. Covered patio has professional misting system and  Heated pool.  Newly landscaped backyard. has lake view from front and back yard The home has surround sound and all LED lights
